Rules.InvariantScript:
"data:image/svg+xml;utf8, " & EncodeUrl(
    "<svg id='Search' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24'>
  <path id='Path_223' data-name='Path 223' d='M0,0H24V24H0Z' fill='none'/>
  <path id='Path_224' data-name='Path 224' d='M15.5,14h-.79l-.28-.27a6.51,6.51,0,1,0-.7.7l.27.28v.79l5,4.99L20.49,19Zm-6,0A4.5,4.5,0,1,1,14,9.5,4.494,4.494,0,0,1,9.5,14Z' fill='" & If(
        galComboboxVauesSS.Visible,
        SearchandSelectComponent.StylingProperty.SearchIcon.FocusColor,
        SearchandSelectComponent.StylingProperty.SearchIcon.Color
    ) & "'/>
</svg>
"
)

If(
    gblComponentGalVisibility,
    "data:image/svg+xml;utf8, " & EncodeUrl(
        "<svg id='Close' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24'>
  <path id='Path_65' data-name='Path 65' d='M0,0H24V24H0Z' fill='none'/>
  <path id='Path_66' data-name='Path 66' d='M19,6.41,17.59,5,12,10.59,6.41,5,5,6.41,10.59,12,5,17.59,6.41,19,12,13.41,17.59,19,19,17.59,13.41,12Z' fill='
  " & SearchandSelectComponent.StylingProperty.CloseIcon.Color & "'/>
</svg>
"
    ),
    "data:image/svg+xml;utf8, " & EncodeUrl(
        "<svg id='Down_Arrow' data-name='Down Arrow' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24'>
  <path id='Path_18' data-name='Path 18' d='M0,0H24V24H0Z' fill='none'/>
  <path id='Path_19' data-name='Path 19' d='M7,10l7,7,7-7Z' transform='translate(-2 -1.5)' fill='
  " & SearchandSelectComponent.StylingProperty.SearchIcon.Color & "'/>
</svg>
"
    )
)

If(
    Self.Visible,
    Min(
        5 * (Self.TemplateHeight + Self.TemplatePadding) + (Self.TemplatePadding * 2),
        CountRows(Self.AllItems) * (Self.TemplateHeight + Self.TemplatePadding) + (Self.TemplatePadding * 2)
    )
)

"data:image/svg+xml;utf8, " & EncodeUrl(
    "<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24'>
  <g id='Up_Stroke_outline' data-name='Up Stroke outline' transform='translate(24) rotate(90)'>
    <path id='Path_95' data-name='Path 95' d='M0,24H24V0H0Z' transform='translate(0 0)' fill='none'/>
    <path id='Path_96' data-name='Path 96' d='M6,7.41l-6-6L1.41,0,6,4.58,10.59,0,12,1.41Z' transform='translate(6 8.59)' fill='" & If(
        btnPrevIconHoverSS.Pressed || btnPreviousSS.Pressed,
        "#fff",
        "#fff"
    ) & "'
    />
  </g>
</svg>
"
)

"data:image/svg+xml;utf8, " & EncodeUrl(
    "<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24'>
  <g id='Up_Stroke_outline' data-name='Up Stroke outline' transform='translate(24) rotate(90)'>
    <path id='Path_95' data-name='Path 95' d='M0,0H24V24H0Z' transform='translate(0)' fill='none'/>
    <path id='Path_96' data-name='Path 96' d='M6,0,0,6,1.41,7.41,6,2.83l4.59,4.58L12,6Z' transform='translate(6 8)' fill='" & If(
        btnNextIconHoverSS.Pressed || btnNextSS.Pressed,
        "#fff",
        "#fff"
    ) & "'/>
  </g>
</svg>
"
)

txtTextInputSS.Height + galComboboxVauesSS.Height + If(
    lblTitleTextSS.Visible,
    lblTitleTextSS.Height,
    SearchandSelectComponent.StylingProperty.TextInput.Margin
) + SearchandSelectComponent.StylingProperty.TextInput.Margin + If(
    btnNavigationBackgoundSS.Visible,
    btnNavigationBackgoundSS.Height
)

With(
    {DropDownComponent: gblControlStyles.SearchandSelect},
    {
        Label: gblControlStyles.ControlLabel,
        TextInput: DropDownComponent,
        CloseIcon: gblControlStyles.CloseIcon,
        SearchIcon: gblControlStyles.SearchIcon,
        Items: DropDownComponent.ItemLabel,
        Separator: DropDownComponent.Separator,
        Checkbox: DropDownComponent.Checkbox,
        NavigationButton: DropDownComponent.NavigationButton,
        NavigationIcon: DropDownComponent.NavigationIcon
    }
)
